## staticPages.module.js

**Summary:** Declares the `staticPagesModule` AngularJS module with no dependencies. Serves as the container for all static informational page controllers (project info, rules, collaborators, terms, prohibited articles, troubleshooting, wrong email link, confirmation success).

**Dependencies:**
- None

**Tags:** static-pages, module

**Implementation:** app/app/pages/staticPages/staticPages.module.js
